snippet.title: Best VGM 1371 - Double Dragon Neon - Lab 2 (Pick Yourself Up and Dance)
snippet.description:
Get the album @ http://virt.bandcamp.com/album/double-dragon-neon

See also:
Best VGM 1213 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vl9Nz-X4M68

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
Double Dragon Neon (2012)
Lab 2 (Pick Yourself Up and Dance)
Jake Kaufman
